function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)
	
--Separating this callback out so these only run once.	
	--remove barrier
	Hydra.EventSend("DRLG_Door_Lock_Sigil_Deactivate_01")
	
	--spawn ambush	
	DF_Ambush("Ambush", "Fly", idActorKiller)
end

unk_c47e01a.value:
function UF_PickAmbushFamily()

	local nRandom = Hydra.GetRandomFloat()
	if nRandom < 0.33 then
		return "Zombie"
	else
		return "Fly"
	end
		
end
